"3/4 cup uncooked orzo","2 teaspoons olive oil","2 teaspoons grated lemon rind","2  garlic cloves, minced","1/4 cup chopped fresh basil","2 tablespoons (1/2 ounce) grated Parmigiano-Reggiano cheese","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon black pepper","  Basil sprigs (optional)"